CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 19, 1958, pg. 22, reads: "Harper At Press Club - Pittsburgh bandleader Walt Harper and jazz enthusiast Sam Hood of the Pittsburgh Press editorial staff swapped piano playing secrets when Harper's combo played a jazz concert at the Pittsburgh Press Club last Saturday night. Hood, a local newsman, owns an imposing collection of jazz records. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Walt Harper playing piano with Sam Hood during jazz concert in Pittsburgh Press Club
